profile: A 70 year old person, living in a married_couple family with 2_person members. The person has 2 vehicles and an annual income of 9192 dollars.
cypher:
MATCH (p:Person)
        WHERE (p.age>60) OR (p.income>=0 AND p.income<30000)
        WITH p ORDER BY rand() LIMIT 50
        MATCH (p)-[r1:WANT_TO]-(d:Desire {desire:'Shop'})-[r2:GO_TO]-(i:Intention)
        RETURN COLLECT(DISTINCT p) AS person, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT d) AS desire, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT i) AS intention,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r1) AS want_to,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r2) AS go_to

        WHERE (p.age>=30 AND p.age<40) OR (p.income>=90000 AND p.income<120000)
        WITH p ORDER BY rand() LIMIT 50
        MATCH (p)-[r1:WANT_TO]-(d:Desire {desire:'Shop'})-[r2:GO_TO]-(i:Intention)
        RETURN COLLECT(DISTINCT p) AS person, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT d) AS desire, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT i) AS intention,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r1) AS want_to,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r2) AS go_to

        WHERE (p.age>=40 AND p.age<50) OR (p.income>=120000)
        WITH p ORDER BY rand() LIMIT 50
        MATCH (p)-[r1:WANT_TO]-(d:Desire {desire:'Shop'})-[r2:GO_TO]-(i:Intention)

profile: A 33 year old person, living in a married_couple family with 2_person members. The person has 1 vehicles and an annual income of 141420 dollars.
cypher:
MATCH (p:Person)
        WHERE (p.age>=30 AND p.age<40) OR (p.income>=120000)
        WITH p ORDER BY rand() LIMIT 50
        MATCH (p)-[r1:WANT_TO]-(d:Desire {desire:'Shop'})-[r2:GO_TO]-(i:Intention)
        RETURN COLLECT(DISTINCT p) AS person, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT d) AS desire,

            COLLECT(DISTINCT r1) AS want_to,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r2) AS go_to

profile: A 20 year old person, living in a family_single family with 3_person members. The person has 1 vehicles and an annual income of 2160 dollars.
cypher:
MATCH (p:Person)
        WHERE (p.age>=18 AND p.age<30) OR (p.income>=0 AND p.income<30000)
        WITH p ORDER BY rand() LIMIT 50
        MATCH (p)-[r1:WANT_TO]-(d:Desire {desire:'Shop'})-[r2:GO_TO]-(i:Intention)
        RETURN COLLECT(DISTINCT p) AS person, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT d) AS desire, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT i) AS intention,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r1) AS want_to,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r2) AS go_to

        WHERE (p.age>=18 AND p.age<30) OR (p.income<0)
        WITH p ORDER BY rand() LIMIT 50
        MATCH (p)-[r1:WANT_TO]-(d:Desire {desire:'Shop'})-[r2:GO_TO]-(i:Intention)
        RETURN COLLECT(DISTINCT p) AS person, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT d) AS desire, 
            COLLECT(DISTINCT i) AS intention,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r1) AS want_to,
            COLLECT(DISTINCT r2) AS go_to
